title: Na matchhistory Website filter wont work
body: I try to sort the match history by a certain champion and press go but nothing happens been doing it for the past week

replies.body: Were you trying to view your own match history for certain types of queues as well? Make sure to leave the match type on all if you're looking at someone elses match history. If that's still not working, trying [**clearing your browser history and cookies**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies) or opening that page in a different browser to see if that helps.
